title: clear_selected_folders()
brief: Clear all selected folders.
----

<p><tt>luamil</tt> allows you to select multiple folders to open at the same time.</p>
<p>The <tt>clear_selected_folders()</tt> function allows you to unselect all currently selected folders.</p>
<p class="seealso">See also <a href="add_selected_folder.html">add_selected_folder()</a>, <a href="selected_folders.html">selected_folders()</a>, <a href="toggle_selected_folder.html">toggle_selected_folder()</a>, <a href="set_selected_folder.html">set_selected_folder()</a>.